data.description: Wow! Don't miss out on this gorgeous home in the beautiful, gated community that is Gold Creek Estates!! Located in the foothills and only miles from New Hogan Lake, this property boasts an open concept with a combined living and dining room, wood look tile, a soaking tub + walk-in closet in the master bathroom, a finished garage, and a backyard ready for entertaining. This home has lots of parking space in the extra-long driveway and sits further from the road for additional privacy- bonus! So much to enjoy with the HOA: Walking/bike trails, pool, gym (new equipment), recreational facility + front yard maintenance! Love golfing? This property is minutes away from La Contenta Golf Course!!
